dc_description_s: The Metro Transit schedule data includes bus and LRT schedules for the Twin Cities metropolitan area. This includes data for all public transit companies in the Minneapolis / St. Paul metropolitan area except the Minnesota Valley Transit Authority. The data uses the General Transit Feed Specification. This specification can be found at https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs/reference?csw=1.
dc_relation_sm: bus routes, bus segments, bus service, bus shelters, park & rides, bus stops For information comparing the different transit GIS datasets distributed by the Met. Council, please see http://www.datafinder.org/metadata/transit_data_overview.pdf .
dc_title_s: Metro Transit Schedule Data, General Transit Feed Specification (GTFS): Twin Cities Metro, Minnesota, 2016
